Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1

(4 comments)

The rest is pretty much optimizations and fine tuning, but I definitely thing we should not transition image state anywhere while we are copying the data between stores.

Worst case scenarios this might take hours and there is no way to consume the image meanwhile. Evacuations/migrations would just fail as the image is not "active".

Patch Set 1:

(4 comments)

Hi Erno,

Thank you for review, I will work on your suggestions.
At the moment I will use the base patch of import multiple stores as it is, till it will be modified with your suggestions.
